# LineProtocol

`text/plain` is the content type for line protocol. `UTF-8` is the default character set.

**Properties**

| Name                     | Type   | Required | Description                 |
| :----------------------- | :----- | :------- | :-------------------------- |
| TEXT_PLAIN               | String | ✅       | "text/plain"                |
| TEXT_PLAIN_CHARSET_UTF_8 | String | ✅       | "text/plain; charset=utf-8" |
